title: BoardGameGeek Hotness
content:
1. **Dice Horde**
*2026*
Roll & Write meets Tower Defense!
![Dice Horde](toplist_images/bgg_001721d1.jpg)

2. **Concordia**
*2013*
Merchants build and trade throughout the Roman Empire to please the Gods.
![Concordia](toplist_images/bgg_f5770c5a.jpg)

3. **Brass: Pittsburgh**
*2026*
Take part in the United States' late 19th-century industrial boom.
![Brass: Pittsburgh](toplist_images/bgg_62a8cf62.jpg)

4. **Magical Athlete**
*2025*
Pit a cast of crazy characters against each other in a madcap race to the finish.
![Magical Athlete](toplist_images/bgg_6003425c.png)

5. **Limit**
*2025*
Lead your nation in the world system.
![Limit](toplist_images/bgg_899d55ee.jpg)

6. **The Old King's Crown**
*2025*
Out-manoeuvre your rivals as you vie for control of an ancient, crumbling kingdom.
![The Old King's Crown](toplist_images/bgg_72d2c899.jpg)

7. **Labyrinth: Chronicles**
*2026*
New take on the all-time classic. Explore the 3D Labyrinth, and help the villagers!
![Labyrinth: Chronicles](toplist_images/bgg_8785ee50.png)

8. **SETI: Search for Extraterrestrial Intelligence**
*2024*
Search for signs of alien life by launching probes and analyzing distant signals.
![SETI: Search for Extraterrestrial Intelligence](toplist_images/bgg_87cefa6e.jpg)

9. **Speakeasy**
*2025*
Earn money running a Manhattan speakeasy business during Prohibition.
![Speakeasy](toplist_images/bgg_8cabba8c.jpg)

10. **Almighty**
*2027*
Perform mighty acts upon hapless mortals to earn belief and glory.
![Almighty](toplist_images/bgg_01d91765.png)

11. **Nippon: Zaibatsu**
*2026*
Control conglomerates of companies driving Japan’s economy.
![Nippon: Zaibatsu](toplist_images/bgg_f9548d55.png)

12. **Cozy Stickerville**
*2026*
Build your village with over 800 stickers! 
![Cozy Stickerville](toplist_images/bgg_1055c13f.png)

13. **Heat: Pedal to the Metal**
*2022*
Push your car to the limit in the pursuit of victory, but don’t overheat!
![Heat: Pedal to the Metal](toplist_images/bgg_52086e6b.png)

14. **The Lord of the Rings: Fate of the Fellowship**
*2025*
As members of The Fellowship, embark on a journey to save—or doom—Middle-earth.
![The Lord of the Rings: Fate of the Fellowship](toplist_images/bgg_70415347.png)

15. **Brass: Birmingham**
*2018*
Build networks, grow industries, and navigate the world of the Industrial Revolution.
![Brass: Birmingham](toplist_images/bgg_2978e6de.jpg)

16. **Hot Streak**
*2025*
Which mascot will cross the finish line first? Who will be DQ'd?
![Hot Streak](toplist_images/bgg_69b2c36f.jpg)

17. **Eternal Decks**
*2025*
Can you solve each stage before your deck runs out?
![Eternal Decks](toplist_images/bgg_2f61d152.png)

18. **Ark Nova**
*2021*
Plan and build a modern, scientifically managed zoo to support conservation projects.
![Ark Nova](toplist_images/bgg_3991c556.jpg)

19. **Tigris & Euphrates**
*1997*
Keep your Mesopotamian civilization in perfect balance through revolutions and wars.
![Tigris & Euphrates](toplist_images/bgg_3b4291d8.png)

20. **High Frontier 4 All**
*2020*
Use real rocket science in a race to industrialize the solar system.
![High Frontier 4 All](toplist_images/bgg_1ce09361.png)

21. **Spirit Island**
*2017*
Island Spirits join forces using elemental powers to defend their home from invaders.
![Spirit Island](toplist_images/bgg_f5dd6a42.jpg)

22. **Andromeda's Edge**
*2024*
Factions clash on the edge of the galaxy!
![Andromeda's Edge](toplist_images/bgg_5111b59b.jpg)

23. **Endeavor: Deep Sea**
*2024*
Lead your research institute to explore ocean depths and publish your findings!
![Endeavor: Deep Sea](toplist_images/bgg_6596f236.jpg)

24. **Arcs**
*2024*
Rule the galaxy with your court, fleet, and cities.
![Arcs](toplist_images/bgg_9614b1c5.png)

25. **Harmonies**
*2024*
Create your own landscape and habitats to welcome animals.
![Harmonies](toplist_images/bgg_502f6048.png)
